{"prompt": "Develop a site for an experimental theatre company. The visuals should be avant-garde and include a vibrant yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>The Unseen Stage</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0e68c; /* Khaki as a base, hints at yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scroll */\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffd700, #f0e68c); /* Vibrant yellow to khaki gradient */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 3rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 4rem;\n            letter-spacing: 0.2rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #8b4513; /* SaddleBrown for section titles */\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            position: relative;\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 50%;\n            bottom: 0;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 100px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: #ffd700; /* Vibrant yellow underline */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Slightly transparent white */\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: justify;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n        }\n        .play-card {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 2px dashed #ffd700; /* Dashed yellow border */\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .play-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .play-card h3 {\n            color: #8b4513;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n        }\n        .play-card p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n        .experimental-element {\n            position: relative;\n            display: inline-block;\n            margin: 1rem;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-left: 5px solid #ffd700;\n            animation: glitch 1s infinite alternate;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes glitch {\n            0% { transform: translate(0); }\n            20% { transform: translate(-5px, 5px); }\n            40% { transform: translate(-5px, -5px); }\n            60% { transform: translate(5px, 5px); }\n            80% { transform: translate(5px, -5px); }\n            100% { transform: translate(0); }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Unseen Stage</h1>\n        <p>Where Reality Unravels</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>The Unseen Stage is a collective of artists dedicated to pushing the boundaries of theatrical expression. We explore the liminal spaces between dreams and waking, the spoken and the unspoken, crafting immersive experiences that challenge perception and ignite the imagination. Our work is raw, visceral, and unapologetically experimental.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Upcoming Productions</h2>\n            <div class=\"play-card\">\n                <h3>Echoes in the Void</h3>\n                <p>A non-linear narrative exploring the fragmented memories of a forgotten city. Prepare for a sensory journey unlike any other.</p>\n                <p><strong>Dates:</strong> October 25-27</p>\n                <p><strong>Location:</strong> The Black Box Theatre</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"play-card\">\n                <h3>The Gilded Cage of Self</h3>\n                <p>An introspective piece that dissects the constructs we build around ourselves, questioning identity and freedom.</p>\n                <p><strong>Dates:</strong> November 15-17</p>\n                <p><strong>Location:</strong> Studio 3B</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"container section\">\n            <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>\n            <p>We believe theatre should be more than entertainment; it should be a catalyst for introspection and dialogue. We embrace disruption, seek unconventional forms, and invite audiences to actively participate in the creation of meaning. Every performance is a unique artifact, never to be replicated.</p>\n            <div class=\"experimental-element\">\n                <p>Embrace the Unknown.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Unseen Stage. All rights reserved. Dare to experience.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}